title: Are Gambhir & Shah divided over T20I captaincy?
Rishi Sunak's advice to UK PM Keir Starmer makes Commons crack up

description: Two security personnel were killed and four others injured in an IED blast triggered by Maoists during an anti-Naxalite operation in the forests of Bijapur district. The incident occurred during a joint operation by various security forces in the insurgency-hit Bastar region. The injured jawans are being airlifted for treatment, while reinforcements have been dispatched to the area. Our thoughts are with the families of the martyred jawans and we hope for a swift recovery for the wounded.
title: 2 security personnel killed, 4 injured in IED blast in Chhattisgarh

description: The Department of Telecommunications has suspended operations of V-con Intelligent Security and OneXtel Media for sending fraudulent SMSes. Over 55 million malicious messages were sent since January 2024. DoT orders telecom service providers to take action against the companies. OneXtel Media denies allegations and questions the government's decision.
title: Govt suspends two telemarketing cos over sending 5.5M fraud SMSes

description: At the Republican National Convention, Usha Vance introduced JD Vance as Trump's Vice President running mate. She shared their personal story and his journey from Ohio State via the G.I. Bill to Yale Law, Marine service in Iraq, and overcoming childhood traumas. His role as a millennial GOP leader comes amid concerns over Trump's and Biden's ages.
title: 'Why I love and admire JD': Usha Vance introduces husband at Republican National Convention
Watch: Doctor's timely CPR saves life of 60-yr-old at Delhi airport

description: A 27-year-old chartered accountant and social media influencer tragically died after falling 300ft from a hillock near Kumbhe waterfall in Raigad district. Despite a six-hour search operation and rescue efforts, she did not survive. The incident occurred during a picnic with a group of seven individuals.
title: Mumbai CA and influencer falls off 300-feet hillock near Raigad waterfall while making reel, dies
Why is Nasa cancelling $450 million Moon rover mission

description: BCCI and PCB will clash at ICC meetings in Colombo over India’s Champions Trophy tour to Pakistan in February 2025. Jay Shah will attend the meeting. Matches might shift to UAE or Sri Lanka. PCB’s Mohsin Naqvi will also be present. If India refuse to go to Pakistan for the tournament, the ICC could be forced to mull the possibility of a hybrid model for the tournament, with India playing their matches in UAE or Sri Lanka.
title: Champions Trophy: It's India vs Pakistan again, this time in boardroom

description: The Parman River bridge in Forbesganj block, Araria district, collapsed due to floodwaters. Enayat Khan noted the bridge's closure since 2017 and repairs in 2020-21 by Prabin Kumar. Built in 2008-09, its collapse resulted in the suspension of 15 engineers for negligence. Additionally, Chaitanya Prasad cited ineffective monitoring. Higher officials were informed, and a checklist was sent.
title: Bihar sees 15th bridge collapse in a month

description: In Jaddan Bata village, Doda, two soldiers were injured at 2:00 am in an encounter with terrorists targeting a temporary camp in a school.  The encounter in Jaddan Bata village is part of a larger search operation that was initiated following the killing of four army personnel, including a captain, by terrorists in Desa and nearby forest areas on the night between Monday and Tuesday.
title: Another encounter between security forces & terrorist in J&K's Doda, 2 soldiers injured

description: On July 13, 2002, Ganguly's team chased 326 at Lord's, winning the NatWest Trophy with 3 balls left. An initial 106-run stand by Sehwag and Ganguly, followed by Yuvraj and Kaif's 121-run partnership from 146/5, were crucial. Ganguly learned from Sehwag's aggressive style, solidifying his leadership by managing different player styles, culminating in the iconic shirt wave.
title: What Ganguly learnt from Sehwag about leadership with NatWest win

description: A confrontation between Bigg Boss OTT contestants Sai Ketan Rao and Lovekesh Kataria turned ugly, leading to threats and physical aggression. Ranvir Shorey intervened to prevent violence. The incident has sparked concern as Lovekesh's friend, Lakshay Kaushik, issued public threats against Sai Ketan Rao.
title: Bigg Boss OTT 3 : After Elvish, Lakshay threatens Sai Ketan Rao

description: Few of the lakhs of BJP workers in the politically key state, trying to come to grips with the unexpected reverses in LS polls, would have found the statements to be problematic. However, if none of them is amused, it is because of the not-so-subtle message driven home and the backdrop of the feud that the party's underwhelming performance has sparked.
title: BJP's UP reverses spark feud as party eyes course correction
